# The Dockerfiles under Docker/ all `COPY . .` from the repository root, so
# anything not excluded here is uploaded as build context and baked into the
# builder layer. `target/` alone is hundreds of megabytes and is rebuilt inside
# the image anyway.
target/
**/target/
Cargo.lock
**/Cargo.lock

.git/
.github/
.idea/
.run/
.env
.secrets
.local/

coverage/
cobertura.xml
tarpaulin-report.html
*.profraw
*.zip

**/.DS_Store
**/*.rs.bk
